snippet.textDisplay: The iPad is most definitely a computer. It’s a shame that Apple has created an advertising campaign that calls this fact into question. There is no question as to whether it can replace a laptop. It has for countless people, even since it’s introduction. With the latest OS it can replace laptops for about 90 percent of computer users.  It features an alternative way of interacting with a computer that takes some getting used to. Once you do, you will be surprised at how much fun the iPad is to use and how much your productivity can actually increase. The iPad has a way of increasing focus while you’re working. When you go back to a conventional computer, it will feel somewhat dated and mundane.
